  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0db8\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1\u0da5\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0ddc\u0db3 \u0db1\u0dd1\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"It is not good to see the black and white of politicians at this time\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Polonnaru District Member of Parliament Mr. Maithripala Sirisena said that according to the state of the country, it is not appropriate for politicians to see black and white at this time.",
        "He also mentioned that everyone should remove the party colors from their heads at this time.",
        "The former president said that he ruled with the current president for five years and that he knows his personality and he knows his personality very well.",
        "He said this in an inquiry made by a group of journalists regarding the all-party government."
      ],
